      - <Q-id, current score>: <what a brilliant human would do
        that I haven't, in one sentence>
      - <Q-id, current score>: <same>
      - <Q-id, current score>: <same>
      (At least 3 lines required by the mission-bar-met gate.)
    Considered but didn't:   <a more radical alternative you
                             considered for one of these and
